ivardefs.name: active
ivardefs.desc:
Whether this patient record is in active use. 
Many systems use this property to mark as non-current patients, such as those that have not been seen for a period of time based on an organization's business rules.

It is often used to filter patient lists

ivardefs.name: birthDate
ivardefs.desc: The date of birth for the individual.

ivardefs.name: communication_
ivardefs.desc: A language which may be used to communicate with the patient about his or her health.

ivardefs.name: contact_
ivardefs.desc: A contact party (e.g. guardian, partner, friend) for the patient.

ivardefs.name: gender
ivardefs.desc: Administrative Gender - the gender that the patient is considered to have for administration and record keeping purposes.

ivardefs.name: link_
ivardefs.desc: Link to another patient resource that concerns the same actual patient.

ivardefs.name: managingOrganization
ivardefs.desc: Organization that is the custodian of the patient record.

ivardefs.name: maritalStatus
ivardefs.desc: This field contains a patient's most recent marital (civil) status.

ivardefs.name: name_
ivardefs.desc: A name associated with the individual.

ivardefs.name: telecom_
ivardefs.desc: A contact detail (e.g. a telephone number or an email address) by which the individual may be contacted.

properties.desc: Demographics and other administrative information about an individual or animal receiving care or other health-related services.
